author_ssm: Megan O'Shea, Jennipher Ambrose, Molly A. Cross, and Alexa Logush
unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Foreign Politics Serials
abstract_ssm: The Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Foreign Politics Serials contains over 300 titles on politics in Europe, Canada, Asia, Latin America, Africa, and Oceania as well as international issues.  The collection dates between 1850 and 2011, with the bulk of the material dating from the 1940s through 1980s.  Topics include politics within countries other than the United States, issues in the Middle East and the Soviet Union in the early to mid-20th century, Palestinian independence movements, and the Cold War.
